-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-9a766e76 dropcap--none sc-ebFjAB ebQNGs" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-d7ea2229 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">C</span><span class="pf-5ae62b0e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">BD is becoming more popular than ever. People are using CBD for fibromyalgia, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5rL1U2eNIOY" target="_self">anxiety</a>, depression, psoriasis, period pain, menopause and more. In this blog, we are going to look at how CBD could be helpful to those suffering from fibromyalgia. We will let you know whether it is worth giving it a try and how it might help you. We will also share some insight into exactly what CBD is so you know what you are taking.&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-03c81c1a pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-8a8009ed sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-2fff3c6e sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-e293bad4 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">What is Fibromyalgia?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-132e910c sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-1ce19ddc sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">The condition fibromyalgia (FMS) causes pain in the whole body. Other symptoms include headaches, IBS, tiredness, muscle stiffness, low pain threshold and concentration problems. Frustratingly, there is no cure at the moment for those who suffer from fibromyalgia. However, medications can help ease symptoms and make the condition a little easier.&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-a83762bd sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-32c08fae sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">What is CBD?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-208af307 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-62bfe74f sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Cannabidiol (CBD) is a cannabinoid found in the cannabis plant. This is, however, legal. CBD does not contain any or enough THC to have psychoactive effects. It is THC which is the banned substance, hence why cannabis is illegal here in the UK and around the world. CBD has been said to have a number of properties which can interact with the human body to help with conditions and illnesses. It has been used as an alternative medicine for thousands of years.&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-f7152e26 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-4f2deda6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">CBD for Fibromyalgia<br></span></h3><p class="pf-ad15af52 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-e2ccb9cb sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">There is ongoing research on CBD for fibromyalgia and lots of anecdotal evidence from customers. CBD has shown promise in relieving some of the symptoms which you may suffer with. These symptoms include sleep disorders, anxiety and pain<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Pain</span> <br>CBD helps pain because of the way in which CBD interacts with the human endocannabinoid system. The cannabinoid interacts with receptors and enhances brain chemicals, such as serotonin. <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/cbd-eliquid" target="_self">When vaped</a> or taken in another form, CBD has been said to interrupt the nerve pathways that send signals of pain between the brain and the body.<br><br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Sleep disorders</span> <br>CBD can help with insomnia and other sleep disorders. Not only that, but you can also use CBD to help you remain alert. That sounds counterproductive, however, it all depends on the type of CBD and how much to take. You may also find that with anxiety and pain levels reduced you can get to sleep a little easier. <br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Anxiety</span> <br>If you suffer from anxiety alongside fibromyalgia then CBD products could be helpful. There have been lots of studies on CBD and anxiety which show how it can reduce your anxiety levels. We have put together an informative <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5rL1U2eNIOY" target="_self">video about anxiety and CBD, watch it here.</a><br><br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-dfa6b302 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-741294a8 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Research is ongoing<br></span></h3><p class="pf-58abecac sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-224925b9 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">There is ongoing research into CBD for fibromyalgia. However, what we have seen so far in terms of it helping with pain, sleep and anxiety, it looks promising. If you are someone who suffers from the condition it could be worth a try. Make sure you check that it won't interfere with your current medications by asking your doctor or an alternative medicine practitioner. <br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-3ad130a2 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-823e01b3 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-a6c1c53e sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-449f0cc2 products pf-r pf-r-ew pf-r-ew--4 sc-jdeSqf bmQTcU" data-animation="pulse" data-pf-type="Shopify.Products">{% assign collection = collections['cbd-eliquid'] %}{% paginate collection.products by 4 %}{% for product in collection.products %}   {% assign prod_id = forloop.index | plus:paginate.current_offset %}<div class="pf-c"><div class="pf__shopify-product shopify__product-vertical"><a class="product__thumbnail" href="{{ product.url }}">{% if product.featured_image != blank %}<img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '270x200' , crop: 'center' , scale: 2 }}" alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}">{% else %}<img src="https://a